    <item>
      <title>Roasted Spicy Chicken With Rice</title>
      <link>https://mezpahlan.github.io/blog/2015/02/01/roasted-spicy-chicken-with-rice/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Feb 2015 14:32:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://mezpahlan.github.io/blog/2015/02/01/roasted-spicy-chicken-with-rice/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I spotted this recipe for &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.munchkintime.com/oven-baked-chicken-wings/&#34;&gt;spicy chicken wings&lt;/a&gt; on Google+ and
thought I would give it a go. I wanted to put my own spin on it which is why I opted for chicken legs instead of wings
and modified some of the ingredients. I also didn&amp;rsquo;t want to buy thirty chicken wings! The recipe does use ketchup but
bear with me, it&amp;rsquo;s not that bad.&lt;/p&gt;
